Write a program to add all digits of a given number
For example:
Input Result
345
303
12
6


Solution : 
//Java 
import java.util.*;
public class addAllDig {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner a = new Scanner(System.in);
        int b = a.nextInt();
        int d = 0; // Initialize d to store the sum
        while (b != 0) {
            int c = b % 10;
            d += c;
            b = b / 10;
        }
        System.out.print(d);
    }
}
